: 278}, {\"ngram\": \"NFP\", \"from\": 311, \"to\": 314}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The fact that he has already refused to do so is a negation of democracy.\\\"\", \"from\": 317, \"to\": 391, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The fact\", \"from\": 317, \"to\": 325}, {\"ngram\": \"a negation\", \"from\": 366, \"to\": 376}, {\"ngram\": \"democracy\", \"from\": 380, \"to\": 389}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That is conservative politician Charles de Courson calling on president Macron to respect French political tradition and name the newly selected NFP candidate, Lucie Castets, as prime minister.\", \"from\": 393, \"to\": 586, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 425, \"end\": 443, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charles_de_Courson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Charles de Courson\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charles_de_Courson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charles_de_Courson\"}, {\"begin\": 455, \"end\": 471, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"president Macron\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\"}, {\"begin\": 483, \"end\": 489, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Third_Republic\", \"score\": 0.9997245830787507, \"rank\": 0.00021359558267393736, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Third_Republic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Third_Republic\"}, {\"begin\": 559, \"end\": 566, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Castets_(grape)\", \"score\": 0.5009607382045541, \"rank\": 0.6944444444443503, \"text\": \"Castets\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Castets_(grape)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Castets_(grap